@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 14

title Distance-vector: idee (RIP)

[Router A] as A
[Router B] as B
[Router C] as C
[Destinatie\nRetea X] as X

A -- B
B -- C
C -- X

note right of A
  A stie:
  - distanta pana la X
  - next hop: B
  Nu stie topologia completa.
end note

note right of B
  Ruterele isi trimit periodic
  vectorii de distante (tabele).
end note
@enduml
